- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is another possible category as the paper deals with solving games and establishing lower bounds. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is relevant as the paper discusses the time complexity of solving special classes of games. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses algorithms for solving games, which could be relevant to programming language theory.
